Example of one of the circuits in my new Home Training Program. Looks simple, but the intensity picks up on you and you are going to be challenging stabilizers muscle that you normally don’t train. Think about it, this is going to set you up with an even better foundation to build off of, once we are all back in the gym!
-

node.text:
Huge improvements in the past 7 days!
-
I signed back up at the gym I trained at back in high school and my amateur bodybuilding years in hopes of bringing back that old gritty work hard af attitude!
-
I haven’t touched a dumbbell over 80lbs in 6 months. I felt great today and worked my way up to the 105’s with good control and tempo.
-
I haven’t felt this optimistic in a long time! 🙌🏽
-
All the Glory to God. Thank you for never giving up on me🙏🏽 
-
#yavalabs

node.text:
Shoulders felt GOOD today. Never thought I’d ever be able to say that again!
-
Making progress 🙏🏽
-
@yavalabs thank you for your support. It’s given me a boost in motivation!
-
@yavalabs will available for you all in August! I can’t wait!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jeremy L. Buendia on July 14, 2021. May be an image of 4 people, biceps, people standing and text that says 'R BEYO RAN ALLMAX'.

node.text: Always winning with my baby girl❤️

The progress hasn’t been as fast as I’ve liked but I’m glad I’ve taken some progress photos along the way. because I looked a whole heck of a lot worse than this a few months back. So  needless to say, I’m happy I’m moving in the right direction. 
-
I can be better in every aspect.
So the work must continue. 😤
